    COVID-19 information

    Travel smart. Travel safe.

    Airlines around the world have enacted additional safety measures and adjusted policies to better accommodate travelers. Policies vary by airline.

    More information about COVID-19 and travel.

    Alaska Airlines

    Alaska Saver fares booked before September 8 are cancellable without a fee. Alaska Main and First fares booked before September 8 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee. For all canceled fares, a travel credit will be issued.

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Middle seats unavailable to book (for a limited time).

    Masks required on board, masks provided.

    Pre-flight health screening questions.

    Allegiant Air

    Allegiant flights are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights made within two years).

    Installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Masks required on board, masks provided.

    American Airlines

    American flights booked before September 8 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights through December 31, 2021).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Masks required on board, masks provided.

    Delta

    Delta flights booked before August 31 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights made within one year).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Middle seats unavailable to book (for a limited time).

    Masks required on board.

    Hawaiian Airlines

    Hawaiian flights booked before August 31 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights made within two years).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Middle seats unavailable to book (for a limited time).

    Masks required on board.

    JetBlue

    JetBlue flights booked before September 8 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights made within two years).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Middle seats unavailable to book (for a limited time).

    Masks required on board.

    Southwest

    Southwest flights are always eligible for change or cancellation without a fee.

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Middle seats unavailable to book (for a limited time).

    Masks required on board, masks provided.

    Spirit Airlines

    Spirit flights booked before August 31 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued is valid through May 2021).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Masks required on board.

    United Airlines

    United flights booked before August 31 are eligible for a one-time change or cancellation without a fee (travel credit issued for future flights made within one year).

    Pre-flight cleaning, installation of cabin HEPA filters.

    Masks required on board, masks provided.
